{"id": "ChIJZ4HQtkK5woAREjxEKSU-gzE", "rating": 4.9, "userRatingCount": 179, "displayName": {"text": "Jun Won Dak IG @junwon_la", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJZ4HQtkK5woAREjxEKSU-gzE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21GWFdrVk1kRzAxVjNkd1pFeDRTRXh0V1ZrMVIzYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Our experience here was absolutely fantastic! 🤩 The food offered an explosion of unique tastes, unlike anything I've had before. The service was impeccable, truly top-notch. And the atmosphere? Simply wonderful, a perfect blend of cozy street food vibes with sophisticated high cuisine. 💯 I highly recommend it! Just be sure to reserve in advance, as they only have two tables for two. 💖✨", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Our experience here was absolutely fantastic! 🤩 The food offered an explosion of unique tastes, unlike anything I've had before. The service was impeccable, truly top-notch. And the atmosphere? Simply wonderful, a perfect blend of cozy street food vibes with sophisticated high cuisine. 💯 I highly recommend it! Just be sure to reserve in advance, as they only have two tables for two. 💖✨", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Fabian Szenkier", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/115412170220343670525/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUcUG5uUoJ_AzzkY6WNl5BJxhxIl1BjtxDdUUD-bvWptYv63OrX3A=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-27T03:11:18.457358496Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21GWFdrVk1kRzAxVjNkd1pFeDRTRXh0V1ZrMVIzYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21GWFdrVk1kRzAxVjNkd1pFeDRTRXh0V1ZrMVIzYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b942b6d08167:0x31833e2529443c12"}, {"name": "places/ChIJZ4HQtkK5woAREjxEKSU-gzE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2taSlJGSkJaVEJzWkZaV1prMHlUM2hTVW5wblVuYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Wow, wow, wow, wow, wow. Hole in the wall place with amazing Korean food. Best Samgyetang we've had. Better than the one in the most famous restaurant in Korea. Eun-Daegu - Black Cod Braised black cod was so flavorful and good. Must visit. Take out with only a couple tables.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Wow, wow, wow, wow, wow. Hole in the wall place with amazing Korean food. Best Samgyetang we've had. Better than the one in the most famous restaurant in Korea. Eun-Daegu - Black Cod Braised black cod was so flavorful and good. Must visit. Take out with only a couple tables.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "T K", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105264637435821916256/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJeG0ZR_fbIave8Wu_J_SseHVfvGdJrxuwqM8asd9hbaYHt7w=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-31T17:36:16.015431420Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2taSlJGSkJaVEJzWkZaV1prMHlUM2hTVW5wblVuYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2taSlJGSkJaVEJzWkZaV1prMHlUM2hTVW5wblVuYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b942b6d08167:0x31833e2529443c12"}, {"name": "places/ChIJZ4HQtkK5woAREjxEKSU-gzE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT214bFdteEtZWHBXZEU5cGFsOU1ibmhJU2xGWVJsRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "My husband and I were able to eat in and met the owners who were so kind! The Galbi-jjim was unreal, the portions and quality were worth the price! We also enjoyed the samgye-tang, comforting and delicious as well.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "My husband and I were able to eat in and met the owners who were so kind! The Galbi-jjim was unreal, the portions and quality were worth the price! We also enjoyed the samgye-tang, comforting and delicious as well.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Julia", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109634815163403794606/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJCQMbhhhTkt9YSM-agHhsKmWNLV5qczvyTKEQVry8T5hpI4Q=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-27T20:56:16.574502006Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT214bFdteEtZWHBXZEU5cGFsOU1ibmhJU2xGWVJsRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT214bFdteEtZWHBXZEU5cGFsOU1ibmhJU2xGWVJsRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b942b6d08167:0x31833e2529443c12"}, {"name": "places/ChIJZ4HQtkK5woAREjxEKSU-gzE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pWNGJUaEphak5xYXpkcU5rSmxXVlExTjJkbExXYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Excellent Chinese restaurant with consistently fresh, flavorful dishes and generous portions. Everything we ordered was hot, well-seasoned, and clearly made with care. The menu offers a great variety of classic favorites and house specialties, making it easy to find something for everyone. Service was friendly and efficient, and the food was ready quickly. A reliable spot for both dine-in and takeout — we’ll definitely be back.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Excellent Chinese restaurant with consistently fresh, flavorful dishes and generous portions. Everything we ordered was hot, well-seasoned, and clearly made with care. The menu offers a great variety of classic favorites and house specialties, making it easy to find something for everyone. Service was friendly and efficient, and the food was ready quickly. A reliable spot for both dine-in and takeout — we’ll definitely be back.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Mo Gerhardt", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109533012295490625326/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK5zoOFRvqPmefXiGsgCcA3fVxzFZXOoc_8ieG-FhTvVOd5IA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-08T02:00:01.887489578Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pWNGJUaEphak5xYXpkcU5rSmxXVlExTjJkbExXYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pWNGJUaEphak5xYXpkcU5rSmxXVlExTjJkbExXYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2b942b6d08167:0x31833e2529443c12"}, {"name": "places/ChIJZ4HQtkK5woAREjxEKSU-gzE/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s1RmRIbHVNR2gyUkhsb2FtTnpXazFKVDNacGRWRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "8 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Tried the Samgyetang and Eun-Daegu and both were incredible and truly authentic! This place is such a hidden gem and definitely gives that hole in the wall vibe in the best way. You can really tell the owners care deeply about the food they serve and take pride in their dishes. I love that they only have four items on the menu, it shows how confident they are in their specialties. I’m already planning to come back the next time I’m in LA!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Tried the Samgyetang and Eun-Daegu and both were incredible and truly authentic! This place is such a hidden gem and definitely gives that hole in the wall vibe in the best way. You can really tell the owners care deeply about the food they serve and take pride in their dishes. I love that they only have four items on the menu, it shows how confident they are in their specialties. I’m already planning to come back the next time I’m in LA!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Lauren Jeong", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/118051499641044462160/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK9twL0bg6b45a7En8g5S2ppwBB194ZM7HeXGtPAjnxa6-pmg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-r